
<% content_for :title, "Rental price comparison table" %>

<div id="limited">
  <div class="pricing_table pricing_dark_style pricing_six comparison column_right">

    <div class="header" style="text-align: left;">
        <h3 data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bypostLimited">By Post - <font class="large">Limited</font></h3>
        <h4>Sites that offer limited rentals per month, by post, for a lower monthly fee</h4>
    </div>

    <div style="margin:0 auto;width:700px">

      <ul class="pricing_column_first">
          <li class="pricing_header1"></li>
          <li class="pricing_header2"><span>Provider</span></li>
          <li class="odd">
            <a class="tooltip" href="#">1 Disc
                <span>Mauris ac quam in tortor congue lobortis nec in metus. Donec eget neque felis. Suspendisse lobortis lectus sed sapien pharetra.</span>
              </a>
          </li>
